to flood the market with cocaine 
el tiempo quoted the report as saying the dramatic growth of the 
cocaine market in western europe is fueled by high prices 
the drug is sold in europe for between 27500 and 115000 a 
kilogram compared to between 10000 and 20000 in the united 
states according to the document a kilogram is 22 pounds 
profits from the european business are enormous the report 
added because distributors receive cocaine that is 90 to 94 
percent pure and sell a product that is only 45 percent pure 
the report cited spain as the principal receiver of cocaine from 
latin america and the main trafficking center for drug destined for 
the european markets 
the report also said cocaine laboratories have been discovered 
in spain as well as in france and italy cocaine processing has 
traditionally been confined to colombia but the countrys war 
against the cartels and its crackdown on imports of processing 
chemicals have reportedly forced drug bosses to move some of their 
operations elsewhere 
although for some the detection of these european processing 
centers has not been alarming the facilities certainly are 
providing a supply of hundreds of kilograms the report said 
the enormous expansion of the cocaine business combined with 
the participation of other criminal organizations has reduced the 
importance of the colombian drug barons especially the medellin 
cartel 
the medellin cartel has begun to lose part of its key members 
and along with them part of the power they exercised over world 
distribution networks said the police report 
it estimated that the cartels share of the world cocaine market 
has been reduced from 75 percent to 40 percent 
